item.title: Have your say: How long do you keep your phone for before upgrading?
item.description: I'm curious if upgrade cycles have gotten longer as phone upgrades have gotten more incremental.

item.title: I use this affordable JBL turntable at home and I can’t recommend it highly enough for anyone putting together their first hi-fi system
item.description: If the vinyl revival has you champing at the bit to find an affordable but capable turntable, this model from JBL is a surefire winner – and it's discounted too.

item.title: If I didn't already own the V15 Detect, the V8 Cyclone would be the Dyson I'd get – now just AU$438.30
item.description: The 2025 release of the Dyson V8 cordless vacuum has just dropped to a record-low price, which makes it excellent value and cheaper than buying V11.

item.title: Mark Zuckerberg Tries to Play It Safe in Social Media Addiction Trial Testimony
item.description: The Meta CEO stuck to a playbook of repetitive answers and buzzwords in a landmark trial in Los Angeles on Wednesday.

item.title: This Indian AI startup is claiming victory over Gemini and ChatGPT, here's why
item.description: India-based startup Sarvam AI claims its language-first OCR and speech models outperform Gemini and ChatGPT

item.title: YouTube is now an exhibit at one of the world’s biggest museums — and I'm shocked that 2006 is now considered 'vintage'
item.description: YouTube's watch page from 2006 is being recreated for an exhibit at the V&A museum, and I've never felt so ancient.
